title: Colts' fake punt among NFL's dumbest plays
text: > Sports Colts' fake punt among NFL's dumbest plays FILE - In this Nov. 22, 2012, file photo, New York Jets quarterback Mark Sanchez is hit by New England Patriots defensive end Jermaine Cunningham (96) and Justin Francis (94) during the second half of an NFL football game in East Rutherford, N.J. Earlier in the game, Sanchez ran into the back of teammate Brandon Moore and fumbled the ball, which was recovered by Patriots' Steve Gregory and returned for a touchdown. (AP Photo/Julio Cortez, File)
